{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "0805bc77-d484-4ad1-801f-49c4122ac566",
    "name": "Employee Onboarding MCP Services - Complete Collection (Updated)",
    "description": "UPDATED: Comprehensive Postman collection for all Employee Onboarding MCP Services with correct API endpoints based on actual Mule flow specifications.\n\n## Services Included:\n\n### 1. Agent Broker MCP\n- **Base URL**: https://agent-broker-mcp-server.us-e1.cloudhub.io/api\n- **Purpose**: Central orchestrator for complete employee onboarding workflow\n- **Endpoints**: /health, /mcp/info, orchestration, status tracking, retry operations\n\n### 2. Employee Onboarding MCP\n- **Base URL**: https://employee-onboarding-mcp-server.us-e1.cloudhub.io/api  \n- **Purpose**: Employee lifecycle management and HR processes\n- **Endpoints**: /health, /mcp/info, employee CRUD operations, status management\n\n### 3. Asset Allocation MCP\n- **Base URL**: https://asset-allocation-mcp-server.us-e1.cloudhub.io/api\n- **Purpose**: IT asset management and allocation\n- **Endpoints**: /health, /mcp/info, asset allocation, return, listing, availability\n\n### 4. Notification MCP\n- **Base URL**: https://notification-service-mcp.us-e1.cloudhub.io\n- **Purpose**: Email notification services for onboarding process\n- **Endpoints**: /health, /mcp/info, welcome emails, asset notifications\n\n## Environment Variables:\n- `agent_broker_url`: agent-broker-mcp-server.us-e1.cloudhub.io\n- `employee_onboarding_url`: employee-onboarding-mcp-server.us-e1.cloudhub.io  \n- `asset_allocation_url`: asset-allocation-mcp-server.us-e1.cloudhub.io\n- `notification_url`: notification-service-mcp.us-e1.cloudhub.io\n\nUpdated: 2024-03-02\nVersion: 2.0.0",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_exporter_id": "46229874"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "1. Agent Broker MCP",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Health Check",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test(\"Status code is 200\", function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test(\"Response has JSON body\", function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.be.json;",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test(\"Health status is UP\", function () {",
                  "    const jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData.status).to.eql(\"UP\");",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.globals.set(\"healthStatus\", pm.response.text());"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "https://{{agent_broker_url}}/api/health",
              "protocol": "https",
              "host": ["{{agent_broker_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "health"]
            },
            "description": "Returns the current health status of the agent broker and orchestration capabilities"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Get MCP Server Info",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test(\"Status code is 200\", function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test(\"Response contains server info\", function () {",
                  "    const jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData).to.have.property('name');",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData).to.have.property('version');",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData).to.have.property('tools');",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "https://{{agent_broker_url}}/api/mcp/info",
              "protocol": "https",
              "host": ["{{agent_broker_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "mcp", "info"]
            },
            "description": "Returns comprehensive information about the agent broker MCP server capabilities and integrated services"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Orchestrate Employee Onboarding",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test(\"Status code is 200 or 500 (expected for orchestration)\", function () {",
                  "    pm.expect(pm.response.code).to.be.oneOf([200, 500]);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test(\"Response has JSON structure\", function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.be.json;",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "const jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    pm.test(\"Orchestration completed successfully\", function () {",
                  "        pm.expect(jsonData.status).to.eql('success');",
                  "        pm.expect(jsonData).to.have.property('employeeId');",
                  "    });",
                  "} else {",
                  "    pm.test(\"Orchestration error details provided\", function () {",
                  "        pm.expect(jsonData).to.have.property('error');",
                  "        pm.expect(jsonData).to.have.property('message');",
                  "    });",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n    \"firstName\": \"John\",\n    \"lastName\": \"Smith\",\n    \"email\": \"john.smith@company.com\",\n    \"department\": \"Engineering\",\n    \"position\": \"Senior Software Engineer\",\n    \"startDate\": \"2024-01-15\",\n    \"manager\": \"Sarah Johnson\",\n    \"managerName\": \"Sarah Johnson\",\n    \"managerEmail\": \"sarah.johnson@company.com\",\n    \"orientationDate\": \"2024-01-16\",\n    \"companyName\": \"TechCorp Inc\",\n    \"assets\": [\n        {\n            \"category\": \"LAPTOP\",\n            \"priority\": \"HIGH\"\n        },\n        {\n            \"category\": \"ID_CARD\",\n            \"priority\": \"HIGH\"\n        }\n    ]\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "https://{{agent_broker_url}}/api/mcp/tools/orchestrate-employee-onboarding",
              "protocol": "https",
              "host": ["{{agent_broker_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "mcp", "tools", "orchestrate-employee-onboarding"]
            }
          },
          "response": []
        },
